QuestData.Title: Wake Up, Get Up, Get Out There
QuestData.Description: They need your help!$B$BNot all of the faeries have been turned yet. Some remain prisoner, but they have these masks on their faces....$b$bYou've got to help them! I'm not strong enough to pry off the masks, but you could! You could stop the guards from getting us too!
QuestData.RewardText: You saved my friends!$b$b<Primrose gives you a small grin.>$b$bWe... we make a pretty good team, huh?
